name: Uesugi Kenshin (01/12)
description: Uesugi Kenshin was the daimyo of the Echigo region during the Sengoku period. His real name is Nagao Kagetora, he grew up to be a well-respected daimyo of his time. He once declared himself the reincarnation of Bishamonten, one of the four heavenly kings in Japanese Buddhist beliefs associated with wealth and courage.
